title: Cosmo Oil Yokkaichi FC
text: <a href="Cosmo%20Oil%20Company">Cosmo Oil</a> Yokkaichi F.C. was a Japanese <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Mie%20Prefecture">Mie</a>. The club has played in <a href="Japan%20Soccer%20League">Japan Soccer League Division 2</a> and in the <a href="Japan%20Football%20League%20%281992%E2%80%931998%29">former Japan Football League</a>.
